des:
Listen to daily updates from the Jocko Podcast. You can just say "Alexa, what's my flash briefing". 

Jocko Willink is a retired Navy Seal officer and New York Times Best Seller. Jocko’s ability to lead is unparalleled and has inspired thousands of people all over the world. He is truly a leadership expert who lives and breathes what he preaches.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
